{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_10_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 甘えん坊なうちやけど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam001.m4a",
      "text": "……なんです？　一緒に観られへん事情でも\nあるんですか？　ないですよねぇ、もちろん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What is it? Is there some reason you can't watch together?\nThere isn't one‚ right? Of course not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.9333337784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（優のお母さんからの視線が痛い……）\n（気付いてくれ、優、頼む……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yu's mother's gaze is piercing…）\n（Please notice‚ Yu‚ I'm begging you…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.6000004451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、うちらの動画、よお観て下さい\n今なら隣に美女二人。両手に花やで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ please watch our video carefully.\nRight now you have two beauties next to you. A flower in each hand‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優、くっつかないでくれ！？\nアイドルとマネージャーには適切な距離が……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yu‚ don't get so close!?\nThere should be appropriate distance between idol and manager…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam002.m4a",
      "text": "あら……そないに娘とくっついて……汗も凄いで？\n{user}さん……あんた、ほんまに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my… getting so close to my daughter… and you're sweating terribly?\n{user}-san… you really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8666705449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam003.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ……ふふ……あはは、ほんまにおもろいお人やねぇ\n私らの冗談を、そない真に受けんでええのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fu… fufu… ahaha‚ you're really an amusing person.\nYou don't need to take our jokes so seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6666705449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私らの、冗談……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Your… jokes…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam004.m4a",
      "text": "私はなんにも怒ってませんし、移籍云々も冗談です\nむしろ、優がいつも甘えてるみたいですみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not angry at all‚ and the transfer talk was also a joke.\nRather‚ I'm sorry that Yu is always acting spoiled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.433340009
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、{user}さん本気にしてたん？\nお母さんには全部話してるって言ったやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ {user}-san‚ did you take it seriously?\nI told you I tell my mother everything‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6333382289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.2666733424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちがこうして冗談言ってることも\nおもろい反応してくれるってことも、伝え済みやで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That I joke around like this‚\nand that you give amusing reactions - I've already told her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1666715622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんが本気でうちのこと心配やったら\nとっくにどっかから圧力かけてるに決まってるやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If my mother was seriously worried about me‚\nshe would have applied pressure from somewhere long ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8000048955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2666733424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは確かに……。じゃあつまり、優の冗談に\n久美子さんも乗っかってたってことですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's certainly true… So you mean Kumiko-san\nwas also going along with Yu's jokes…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666715622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam005.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、話の通りおもろいからつい。でも、優が\nのびのび仕事させてもらってるみたいで安心しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ it was amusing as described‚ so I couldn't help it.\nBut I'm relieved that Yu seems to be working freely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam006.m4a",
      "text": "父親が甘やかすもんやから\nこの子ってば、ほんまに甘えん坊に育ってもうて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because her father spoils her‚\nthis child has grown up to be really spoiled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.3000066757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ママ！　うち、そこまで甘えん坊ちゃうで\nそれに、ちゃんと甘える相手は選んでるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mama! I'm not that spoiled.\nBesides‚ I properly choose who to act spoiled with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.2000066757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam007.m4a",
      "text": "けどな、優の冗談を本気にする人もおるんよ\n気を付けんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are people who take Yu's jokes seriously.\nYou need to be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうやけど、うちはちゃんと人を見極めてるで\n{user}さんは、絶対大丈夫や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but I properly judge people.\n{user}-san is absolutely fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333382289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.4333382289
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.4000066757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam008.m4a",
      "text": "それが知れて良かったって話や\nこれからも、優のことよろしゅうお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I'm glad to know.\nPlease continue to take care of Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。優さんのことは、絶対に守ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. I will absolutely protect Yu-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666784286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16933.322842899997,
          "startTime": 171.9000012715
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "鈴村久美子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kumiko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yumam009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、まるで優と結婚でもするみたいな言い方やね\nほな、準備もあるやろうし、見学者は先に行ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're talking like you're going to marry Yu or something.\nWell then‚ you probably have preparations‚ so the observer will go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.9000209171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "ママ……ありがとう\n仕事はきっちりやるから、見とってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mama… thank you.\nI'll do my work properly‚ so please watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2333524703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.7666756312
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……さすが一流の役者さんだ……\nすっかり騙されたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… as expected of a first-class actress…\nI was completely fooled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.2000089645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちもお母さんも、調子に乗り過ぎたみたいやな\n親子共演が嬉しくて、はしゃいでもうて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both my mother and I seem to have gotten carried away.\nWe were happy about the parent-child collaboration and got excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.9666756312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.7000209171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが優しいから\nつい、いつも以上に甘えて、迷惑掛けてもうたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because {user}-san is kind‚\nI ended up acting more spoiled than usual and causing trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3000089645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.1666865665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて、本番前にこんな暗い顔してたらあかんわ\nもう一回台本読んで、シーンの復習しときます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But I shouldn't have such a gloomy face before the performance.\nI'll read the script once more and review the scenes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8666756312,
