      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだ。優が楽しく、そして何よりも\nやりたいことに打ち込めるように、精一杯俺も支えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. So that Yu can enjoy herself‚ and above all\nfocus on what she wants to do‚ I'll support you with all my might.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.9999967575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 241.3666743595
    },
    {
