      "text": "せやったら、今から一つ\nうちのお願い聞いてもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ could you listen to\none request of mine right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.9666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
