      "text": "ほなうちが、じっくりたっぷり介抱してあげますね\nこれも演技の練習ですから、ほらほら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll carefully and thoroughly nurse you.\nThis is also acting practice‚ so come on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.5000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいやいや、何をするつもりだ！？\nそもそも練習ならセリフだけでいいだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no no no‚ what are you planning to do!?\nFor practice‚ just the lines should be enough.",
